00:00.740 --> 00:02.980
Hi welcome to blender 2.8.

00:02.990 --> 00:04.690
Game character creation.

00:04.820 --> 00:10.160
I'm Darren Lyle a Blender Foundation certified trainer and in this course we're going to create this

00:10.160 --> 00:16.940
character and one of the cool things about it is that we're going to incorporate both blenders 3D tools

00:16.940 --> 00:25.340
here and the new 2D grease pencil animation as well so that in one interface we can animate both the

00:25.340 --> 00:29.700
3D body and the 2D face.

00:29.720 --> 00:32.600
