In addition we'll take this character into unity and set him up as a game character so that when we

00:39.260 --> 00:48.050
run the game right here we'll be able to run the character around the environment jump and just have

00:48.050 --> 00:49.690
some fun with him.

00:49.820 --> 00:53.260
