01:00.440 --> 01:07.040
sheets that we create for the 2D base animations we go through a lot of material in this course from

01:07.190 --> 01:16.160
modeling and texturing rigging animation and even writing a C sharp script in unity so the Course does

01:16.160 --> 01:23.300
assume at least some experience with Blender and unity but we'll go through every part of the process

01:23.570 --> 01:24.630
step by step.

01:24.800 --> 01:30.230
So hopefully it's a smooth learning curve right through the end of the process creating a character

01:30.230 --> 01:31.990
